snippet.title: Game & Watch - Manhole (new wide screen) (c)1983 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
[MAME] Game & Watch - Manhole (new wide screen) (c)1983 Nintendo

Emulation once again by algestam
As with Blackjack the artwork was provided by hydef and shows the full case.  This is the new wide screen version from 1983, the original game was 1981.  hydef's artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1IbSRYTfKoKDgZfJZTZdnKFSpBvCvgJZV
The game is similar to titles such as Bridge-It on the Amstrad CPC which was almost certainly influenced by this.
